snippet.title: First Page of Love Prologue
snippet.description: I will NOT be playing this anymore. At first it interested me, and the MC's behavior during the prologue annoyed me, but decided to give it a try. NO. I hate it. This is the worst MC ever, I hate her w/ a passion, and yeah she might change but I can't stand her after reading Lemnas chapter 1 so I won't be continuing it. I won't be posting chapter 1 either due to a malfunction. Plus the names in here are the dumbest thing ever.
